   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Kogi/Kwara Vitamin Support</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The purpose of the project is to eliminate Vitamin A deficiency in children aged 6 to 59 months.

The objectives include:
&#x2022; To build capacity for community based Vitamin A supplementation activities.
&#x2022; To ensure adequate coverage of the target population during Vitamin A supplementation. 
&#x2022; To ensure community members are aware of the importance of Vitamin A supplementation
&#x2022; To ensure adequate record keeping and reporting. 
The key activities include;
&#x2022; Capacity building.
&#x2022; Behavioural change and communication messages.
&#x2022; Community Based Vitamin A supplementation.
&#x2022; Monitoring and evaluation

The aim of the project is to contribute to the reduction of under five mortality</narrative>
  </description>
